  <rdf:type rdf:resource="#Evidence"/>
  <evidenceContent rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">Directory Information Unless you request that your information be withheld to comply with FERPA DCCCD may release information classified as directory information to the general public without the written consent of the student Directory information includes name home address home telephone number email addresses field of study photograph dates of attendance enrollment status i e full-time part-time undergraduate graduate degrees certificates and other honors and awards received the type of award received i e academic technical tech-prep or continuing education participation in officially recognized activities weight and height of members of athletic teams student classification name of the most recent previous institution attended</evidenceContent>
</owl:NamedIndividual>

